quran[71]{c,v,t}:
  80,1,Wo turush ro howa aur mon mor lia
  80,2,(sirf isliey)kay uskay pass ik nabina aya
  80,3,Tujhy kia khabar shayad wo sanwar jata
  80,4,Ya nasehat sunta or usy nesehat fiada phunchati
  80,5,Jo be parwaii kerta hay
  80,6,Uski taraf to pori twaja kerta hy
  80,7,halankay us kay na sanwarney say tujh per koi ilzam nahi
  80,8,Aur jo shaks tery pass dorta hoywa ata hay
  80,9,Aur wo der (bhi) raha hay
  80,10,To us say byrukhi barta hay
  80,11,Yeh thek nahi quran is nasehat (ki chez) hay
  80,12,jo chahy ussy nasehat ly
  80,13,(ye to)purazmat sahifon mein hay
  80,14,Jo buland o bala or pak saf hein
  80,15,Asy likhney walon kay haton mein hy
  80,16,Jo buzurgh or pakbaz hein
  80,17,Allah ki mar insan per kaisa nashukra hay
  80,18,Ussy Allah nay kis chez say paida kiya
  80,19,Ussy ik nutfay say phir andazy per rakha ussko
  80,20,Phir us kay liey rasta asan kiya
  80,21,Phir usy mot di aur phir qabar mein dafan kiya
  80,22,Phir jab chaey ga zinda ker day ga
  80,23,Hergiz nahi unsay ab tak Allah kay hokum ki byja awari nahi ki
  80,24,Insan ko chahye kay apnay khaney ko dekhy
  80,25,Kay hum nay khob pani barsaya
  80,26,Phir phara zamen ko achi tarah
  80,27,Phir is mein anaj ugaey
  80,28,Or angoor or tarkari
  80,29,Aur zeitoon or khajoor
  80,30,Aur gunjan baghat
  80,31,Aur mywa(aur ghass)chara(bhi ugaya)
  80,32,Tumhary istamal o faidy kay liey or tumhary chopayon kay liey
  80,33,Pus jab kay kan bhyray ker dyney wali (qiyamat)ajaey gi
  80,34,Us din admi apnay bhai say
  80,35,Aur apni maa or bap say
  80,36,Aur apni biwi or apni ulad say bhagy ga
  80,37,in mein say her ik ko us din asi fikar(damengeer)hogi jo uskay liey kafi hogi
  80,38,Us din bohat say chehry roshan hongy
  80,39,Jo hansty hoy aur hashshash bashshash hongay
  80,40,Aur baht say chehry usdin ghubar alod hon gay
  80,41,Jis per siyahi charhi hoi hogi
  80,42,wo yehi kafir badkirdar log hon gay
  81,1,Jab sooraj lappet liya jaey ga
  81,2,Aur jab sitary by noor hojaein gay
  81,3,Aur jab pahar chalaye jaein gya
  81,4,Aur jab das mah ki hamla oontniyan chor di jaein gi
  81,5,Aur jab wehshi janwar ikhattay kiey jaein gay
  81,6,Aur jab samander bharka diey jaien gay
  81,7,Aur jab janein (jimson say) mila dein jaein gein
  81,8,Aur jab zinda gari hoi larki say sawal kiya jaey ga
  81,9,Kay kis gunha ki waja say wo qatal ki gae
  81,10,Aur jab nama amal khol diey jaein gay
  81,11,Aur jab asman ki khal utar li jaey gai
  81,12,Aur jab jahanum bharkai jaei gi
  81,13,Aur jab jant nazdek kerdi jaey gi
  81,14,To us din her shaks jan lyga jo kuch yeh ker aya hoga
  81,15,Mein qasam khata hon pechay hatnay waly
  81,16,Chalnay phirney waly chupney waly sitaron ki
  81,17,Aur rat ki jab janey lagy
  81,18,Aur subha ki jab chamek ney lagy
  81,19,Yaqenan yeh ik buzrug rasool ka kaha howa hay
  81,20,Jo qooat wala hay arsh waly (Allah) kay nazdek buland martaba hay
  81,21,Jis ki (asmanon mein)ita-at ki jati hay amen hy
  81,22,Aur tumhara sathi dewana nahi hay
  81,23,isnay us(farishty)ko asman kay kholy kinary per dekha bhi hay
  81,24,Aur yeh ghaib ki baton ko batlaney mein bakhil bhi nahi
  81,25,Aur yeh quran shytan mardod ka kalam nahi
  81,26,Phir tum kahan jarahy ho
  81,27,Yeh to tamam jahan walon kay liey nasehat nama hay
  81,28,(bilkhosos)us kay liey jo tum mein say sedhi rah per chalna chahy
  81,29,Aur tum baghair parwardigar e alam kay chahaye kuch nahi chah saktay